import React, { useContext, useState } from "react"; import sellnowService from "../services/sellnowService"; import { UserContext } from "../contexts/UserContext"; const SellNow = () => { const [brand, setBrand] = useState(``); const [model, setModel] = useState(``); const [productType, setProductType] = useState(``); const [generation, setGeneration] = useState(``); const [touchscreen, setTouchscreen] = useState(``); const [screenSize, setScreenSize] = useState(``); const [graphicsCardModel, setGraphicsCardModel] = useState(``); const [ram, setRAM] = useState(``); const [hdd, setHDD] = useState(``); const [ssd, setSSD] = useState(``); const [message, setMessage] = useState(``); const [laptopImage, setLaptopImage] = useState(null); const user = useContext(UserContext); const handleSubmit = (event) => { event.preventDefault(); const formData = new FormData(); formData.append("brand", pLaptop.brand); formData.append("model", pLaptop.model); formData.append("generation", pLaptop.generation); formData.append("productType", pLaptop.productType); formData.append("touchScreen", pLaptop.touchscreen); formData.append("screenSize", pLaptop.screenSize); formData.append("graphicsCardModel", pLaptop.graphicsCardModel); formData.append("ram", pLaptop.ram); formData.append("hddCapacity", pLaptop.hddCapacity); formData.append("ssdCapacity", pLaptop.ssdCapacity); formData.append("message", pLaptop.message); formData.append("laptopImage", pLaptop.laptopImage); const newLaptop = { brand: brand, model: model, generation: generation, productType: productType, touchscreen: touchscreen, screenSize: screenSize, graphicsCardModel: graphicsCardModel, ram: ram, hddCapacity: hdd, ssdCapacity: ssd, message: message, laptopImage: formData, }; if ( brand !== "" || model !== "" || productType !== "" || generation !== "" || touchscreen !== "" || screenSize !== "" || graphicsCardModel !== "" || ram !== "" || hdd !== "" || ssd !== "" ) { sellnowService.addLaptop(newLaptop, user?.email); setBrand(""); setModel(""); setGeneration(""); setProductType(""); setTouchscreen(""); setScreenSize(""); setGraphicsCardModel(""); setRAM(""); setHDD(""); setSSD(""); setMessage(""); } }; return (
setLaptopImage(e.currentTarget.files[0])} className="form-control" required />
); }; export default SellNow;
